，朱凱迪好似剛剛同林鄭月娥私通了這麼開心雀躍，不知道兩人拖手仔之後，面紅心跳了沒有？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoedGhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoedGhf.jpg&h=af191f54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovNCovB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovNCovB.jpg&h=cbf3176c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqEUqJW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqEUqJW.jpg&h=6862ba15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e18b019c025b82f238743a3cd43952a52f3eb43a","tid":1542581,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:23:28.000Z","msg":"What the fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb6f4fc4829f7977a58251f362edae35d121adf","tid":1542581,"uid":49605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:23:29.000Z","msg":"民主黨<br />\n賣香港"},{"pid":"d6ff0e089141d6d912920a6156e569437b09b4d7","tid":1542581,"uid":311734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"民建聯B隊<br />\n無講錯你啦"},{"pid":"046c9519418755a91f5ecfe11579ff5070e24c8a","tid":1542581,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"班友想燈死邱騰華 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74cd7907ff79a6b2d82d6d70040ab2e3e9e7087","tid":1542581,"uid":306147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"四方西都痴9線，成日胡言亂語<br />\n未睇全文，但係好撚好笑，間接迫9邱騰華出黎跪低"},{"pid":"c92c7452c190db68f2893a00ad50b4abf55ab739","tid":1542581,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f618acbb5aa47d2921b30e099fd545c7abd4d5ca","tid":1542581,"uid":45925,"like":0,